e the house electricity during power outages through the breaker box.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve problems with simple puzzles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456350/extras/a7c9a3a9516adf4fe26247074ce95384.poster.avif?t=1740078446\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456350/extras/a7c9a3a9516adf4fe26247074ce95384.webm?t=1740078446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456350/extras/a7c9a3a9516adf4fe26247074ce95384.mp4?t=1740078446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
